add_key_permission
Disk World creator help
add_key_permission

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_key_permission -  This method adds in a specific permission type into the current permission set for this key.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_key_permission(string group,
string key,
string type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^group%^RESET%^ - the key group to add the permision to
%^BOLD%^key%^RESET%^ - the key to add the permission for
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the permission type to add in
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
0 if it is already added, 1 if not.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/key_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds in a specific permission type into the current
permission set for this key.
.EP

